Love has always been in the air for those who are entwined in marital communion, and they will forever be two in one undisputable rapport. For this wonderful couple, the Ashirus, it has been a long and very remarkable journey of cupid for now over three decades of good matrimony. The former Ogun State Commissioner for Commerce and Industry, Otunba Bimbo Ashiru and his beautiful wife, Kemi are indeed a good copy for those who are wishing to have a good matrimonial life. Celebrating 30 years down the trail in their eventful matrimony, the affair has produced many lovely children, host friends and associates in business and politics sphere, the top society characters, Ashiru and his wife of 30 years, Olukemi went out of their way to make them feel welcome. Among these individuals that were at the Ashiru’s Ikoyi home in Lagos were Kwara State Governor, AbdulRahman AbdulRazaq, Ogun State Governor, Dapo Abiodun; Abiodun’s predecessor, Otunba Gbenga Daniel; top media personalities, Bisi Olatilo, ashorun Dele Momodu and many others. The perfect couple are sure reveling in their marriage because nothing whatever can come in between them, as they have weathered all storms and crossed all obstacles in these thirty years of unfettered love and uncommon relationship. Relishing their love journey, vivacious and ever-charming Kemi said, being the Otunba’s wife for the past three decades has been bliss, due to his charming personality, while also accompanying the photos of their marital union with touching notes wherein she showered praises on her heartthrob of many years, describing him as an exemplary and kind husband.